<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Your Verification Code</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 30px;">
    <table width="100%"
        style="max-width: 600px; margin: auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: center;">
                <h2 style="color: #2c3e50;">Hello {{name}},</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555;">
                    Thank you for using our service.<br>
                    Here is your verification code:
                </p>
                <div style="margin: 20px 0;">
                    <span
                        style="display: inline-block; font-size: 28px; letter-spacing: 6px; font-weight: bold; color: #2c3e50; background: #f0f0f0; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 6px;">
                        {{activationCode}}
                    </span>
                </div>
                <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #999;">This code will expire in 5 minutes.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #999;">If you didn’t request this code, you can safely ignore this
                    email.</p>
                <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee;">
                <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #bbb;">© 2025 EduMarket. All rights reserved.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>